{"id":"bd-3hfp","title":"Gas Town detection inconsistency in migrate_dolt.go","description":"migrate_dolt.go:106 uses raw env var check 'os.Getenv("GT_ROOT") == ""' to detect Gas Town, while main.go:541 uses the centralized doltserver.IsDaemonManaged() function. If the detection logic changes (e.g., filesystem heuristic fallback), migrate_dolt.go won't pick up the change.

Location: migrate_dolt.go line 106 (AutoStart computation in handleToDoltMigration)

Fix: Replace 'os.Getenv("GT_ROOT") == ""' with '!doltserver.IsDaemonManaged()' to match main.go.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"steve.yegge@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-03-01T18:09:07Z","created_by":"beads/polecats/opal","updated_at":"2026-03-01T18:09:07Z"}

