By contrast, verifyMigrationData() (line 205) correctly accepts user/password parameters from the caller.

Fix: Add user and password parameters to verifyServerTarget() and use them in the DSN. Update callers in runMigrationPhases() to pass the configured credentials.","status":"hooked","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"beads/polecats/jasper","owner":"steve.yegge@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-03-01T18:09:13Z","created_by":"beads/polecats/opal","updated_at":"2026-03-01T18:23:19Z"}

