{"id":"bd-rmll","title":"bd migrate --to-dolt blocked in nocgo builds unnecessarily","description":"migrate_dolt_nocgo.go rejects 'bd migrate --to-dolt' with 'Dolt backend requires CGO' error. However, migrate_shim.go already provides a working SQLite extraction path via the system sqlite3 CLI that works without CGO. The auto-migration path (migrate_auto_nocgo.go) correctly delegates to shimMigrateSQLiteToDolt(), but the explicit --to-dolt path does not.

